data.description: OPEN HOUSE FEB 3RD 1-3.  Lovely Brick Twin with covered front Porch,New Front Door to come in to your remodeled Home. Spacious and open floor plan Living RM with Hardwood Floors, freshly painted , new ceiling fans,Electric fireplace, open to your dining room. New half Bathroom on the first floor, Enlarged and remodeled Kitchen ,New Pantry,  you can go out to your 20x22 deck to enjoy the outdoors. New flooring and freshly painted Primary Bedroom and new ceiling fans, walk in closet  2sd bedroom has new flooring , just painted and ceiling fan. Main bathroom has been updated.  Walk up attic and Full Basement with laundry room and half bath.  Nice big double level yard.   Seller leaving 3 window air conditioners.   Motivated Sellers , will consider any reasonable offers.
